      <title><![CDATA[hexo d 报错]]></title>
      <url>/2017/11/30/hexo-d-%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="执行命令-hexo-d时报如下错误："><a href="#执行命令-hexo-d时报如下错误：" class="headerlink" title="执行命令 hexo d时报如下错误："></a>执行命令 hexo d时报如下错误：</h3><p>could not read Username for ‘<a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com</a>‘: Invalid argument</p>
<h3 id="解决方案："><a href="#解决方案：" class="headerlink" title="解决方案："></a>解决方案：</h3><p>输入命令：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config --global core.autocrlf <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>然后执行：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean </span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>若还是报错，就再执行一遍 hexo clean ，hexo g，hexo d</p>
]]></content>
      
